Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}...right?{だよね？\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A-Ah, I was just reading from Shin'ichi-{\i1}niichan{\i0}'s e-mail...{Right now I was [just] reading what Shin'ichi-niichan had written in his mail...あっ　今のは　新一兄ちゃんのメールを読んだだけで…。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh come on, don't scare me like that!{Sheesh, don't startle me like that!もぉ～！\Nビックリさせないでよ～！\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Your face even looks like his...{[Because] even your faces look similar!ただでさえ\N顔が似てるんだから～。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm sorry...{ご　ごめんなさい。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What a shame.{Still... what a shame, right?でも　残念よね？\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Even though the case is finally solved,{Even we solved this case we were highly anticipating,せっかく\N今回の事件　解けたのに→\N} we still don't know who the thief was...{we don't know who the thief was...窃盗犯が\Nわからないなんて。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:20:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Maybe this bloody ¥10 coin I found under the vending machine could be a clue.{[Perhaps] this 10-yen coin with blood I found underneath the vending machine could be a clue.手がかりなら\Nこの自販機の下から→\N} {血の付いた\N１０円玉を見つけたよ。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If it's got blood on it, that means...{Huh? If it has blood in it, could that mean...え？\N血が付いてるってことは…。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah. When the thief took the coins,{Yeah. When the offender took the coins,ああ　きっと　犯人が\N小銭を拾った時に→\N} they probably dropped this one and it went under the vending machine.{this one probably got dropped and ended up beneath the vending machine.取り損ねて　自販機の下に入ったんだろうけど→\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But if the fingerprints on this match any from previous offences...{We'll probably get a match if we compare the fingerprints on it with [that of previous convicts / the criminal records].これに付いた指紋に\N前科があったとしたら。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}They sure do!{You will!・あるぜ！・\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Assault...{Assault...・暴行…・\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}ABH...{Battery...・傷害…・\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Blackmail...{[And] extortion...・恐喝…・\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Altogether, that's three previous offences.{Three people with three previous convictions.ヘヘッ…\N３人まとめて前科３犯だ。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh wait... Theft makes that four.{Well, we'd have to add theft to that, making it four.おっと　窃盗も入れると\N４犯になっちまう。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So won't you give that back to us?{Then... won't you give it back to us?だからさぁ\N返してくれねぇかな？\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You can spare ¥10, right?{It'll be fine since it's [just] 10 yen, right?１０円ぐらい　いいだろ？\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then after that, the three of us'll show you our 'love' all at once.{null.AR: This probably needs reviewing, but it's the best I could come up with after getting a hand from bluesun}{Once the three of us are done showing you our love [together].{後で　３人まとめて\Nかわいがってやるからよ。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Okay...{オッケー。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Take it!{おっ？\N受け取りな！\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey!{おいっ！\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Damn! What'd ya do that for!{Damn! What [are you / do you think you're] doing?!{クソッ！何しやがんだ！！\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Damn it!{ヘヘッ…。\Nクソッ！\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You brat!{ガキがぁ～！！\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You bastards... Gimme a break!{て　てめぇら　ふざけんな！\N}
