Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That ball... Was that you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?{That ball... was it [you / yours], Conan-kun?{あっ　あ　あのボール\Nコナン君？\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Huh? Uh, y-yeah...{えっ？あっ　う　うん…。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Huh? You're not going to the police station?{Huh? you won't come with us to the police?{え？世良さん\N警察に行かないの？\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah. Sorry about that. Could you do the questioning without me?{Nah, sorry for that. I'll leave the police questioning up to you [lot].{ああ　悪いけど→\N\N事情聴取は\N君らだけで受けてくれ。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's something that I have to do, so I've gotta be going.{I'll have to pass on that [task]. Excuse me, but I'll go [ahead].{僕は　外せない用があるから\Nお先に失礼させてもらうよ。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}O-Okay...{う　うん…。\N}
