Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It'd be bad if it got infected.{It'd be bad if bacteria got in[to you / through there].{バイキン入ったら大変だもん。\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, right... I'm sorry.{[Yeah,] I'm sorry.{あ　うん…　ごめんなさい。\N}
